OL,6,FThe Welsh Index of Multiple
OL,7,FDeprivation (WIMD) identifies areas
OL,8,Fwith the highest concentrations of
OL,9,Fseveral different types of
OL,10,Fdeprivation, and is the official
OL,11,Fmeasure of relative deprivation for
OL,12,Fnearly 2,000 small areas in Wales,
OL,13,Fwhich are all ranked.
