OL,6,FWIMD is ranked according to eight
OL,7,Fdifferent types of deprivation -
OL,8,Fcalled domains - including income,
OL,9,Femployment, health, education, access
OL,10,Fto services, housing, physical
OL,11,Fenvironment and community safety, and
OL,12,Fis used to inform public policy and
OL,13,Fwhere to target resources and services.
OL,15,FThe Welsh Government website said:
OL,16,F"Being deprived does not just mean
OL,17,Fbeing poor, it can also mean having
OL,18,Ffewer resources and opportunities than
OL,19,Fwe might expect in our society, for
OL,20,Fexample in terms of health, education
OL,21,For access to services."
